name: r-smartsva

owner.description: Bioconda is a distribution of bioinformatics software realized as a channel for the versatile Conda package manager.
owner.name: bioconda

summary: Introduces a fast and efficient Surrogate Variable Analysis algorithm that captures variation of unknown sources (batch effects) for high-dimensional data sets. The algorithm is built on the 'irwsva.build' function of the 'sva' package and proposes a revision on it that achieves an order of magnitude faster running time while trading no accuracy loss in return.
